23:50.710 --> 23:51.610
- Oh, hell no.

23:51.610 --> 23:53.090
- You know the business is dwindling.

23:53.090 --> 23:54.820
So you've got all these rules.

23:54.820 --> 23:56.920
No fucking samples.

23:56.920 --> 23:59.030
No fucking kids.

23:59.030 --> 24:01.140
This place is thriving with families.

24:01.140 --> 24:04.460
- We really don't wanna
have crying kids here.

24:04.460 --> 24:07.180
I just would like to have a quiet getaway

24:07.180 --> 24:11.710
for our honeymooners and
birthdays and anniversaries.

24:11.710 --> 24:13.040
- A honeymoon venture, they come down

24:13.040 --> 24:16.190
