and eat a frozen burger?

24:16.190 --> 24:17.460
Come on.

24:17.460 --> 24:19.360
This place is haemorrhaging money.

24:19.360 --> 24:20.990
'Cause you're caught in a web.

24:20.990 --> 24:24.233
Delusional, stubborn, old-fashioned,

24:25.432 --> 24:26.823
