24:27.830 --> 24:28.733
- Anything else?

24:30.140 --> 24:31.200
- It's just a joke for you, isn't it?

24:31.200 --> 24:35.293
- No, next time I'm gonna
know to do a little dusting.

24:36.660 --> 24:38.420
- Wow, a little dusting.

24:38.420 --> 24:39.913
Fuck me, how deluded.

24:42.915 --> 24:45.665
(dramatic music)

24:48.240 --> 24:49.510
During dinner service,

24:49.510 --> 24:51.950
I decided to do some
investigating in the rooms.

24:51.950 --> 24:53.560
Dreadful, dreadful, dreadful.

24:53.560 --> 24:54.880
And after what I found,

24:54.880 --> 24:58.000
