25:11.980 --> 25:13.010
- [Brent] I can't see a darn thing.

25:13.010 --> 25:13.843
- [Gordon] You can't see?

25:13.843 --> 25:15.540
Maybe Afni.

25:15.540 --> 25:16.373
- Yeah.

25:16.373 --> 25:18.820
- [Gordon] Explain to Brent what this is.

25:18.820 --> 25:20.040
- [Afni] Spot.

25:20.040 --> 25:21.480
- [Gordon] Spot, you don't know?

25:21.480 --> 25:22.808
- [Afni] Yeah, spot.

25:22.808 --> 25:25.250
- [Gordon] Maybe this one
