washed one week ago.

25:49.510 --> 25:50.343
Every single one of them.

25:50.343 --> 25:51.230
- Absolute rubbish.

25:51.230 --> 25:53.210
And look at this!

25:53.210 --> 25:54.290
I mean, these customers,

25:54.290 --> 25:55.990
