- Stop!

26:00.200 --> 26:01.033
- We have-

26:01.033 --> 26:02.040
- You cannot be serious!

26:02.040 --> 26:04.550
- We are serious, it
was done and that's it.

26:04.550 --> 26:05.383
We're not gonna

26:05.383 --> 26:06.261
sit here and-
- I swear, I got the receipt.

26:06.261 --> 26:08.240
- [Gordon] Right, but that is not clean.

26:08.240 --> 26:10.650
- Oh, that's bullshit.
- Yeah, it is bullshit!

26:10.650 --> 26:12.200
- And this...

26:12.200 --> 26:13.440
Go on.

26:13.440 --> 26:16.280
- [Brent] I see that, but one
week ago, that was cleaned.

26:16.280 --> 26:17.970
- I'm done with this bullshit.

26:17.970 --> 26:19.440
This is from years!

26:19.440 --> 26:20.670
- We did 13 of them

26:20.670 --> 26:21.653
one week ago.
- Stop lying!

26:21.653 --> 26:23.480
- [Brent] Then they're not
cleaning them properly.

26:23.480 --> 26:26.693
- Stop, just for once
today, fucking lying!

26:28.216 --> 26:30.883
(intense music)

26:34.250 --> 26:36.300
And look at this.

26:36.300 --> 26:38.150
I mean, that is not cleaned.

26:38.150 --> 26:40.020
- [Brent] That was just
washed one week ago.

26:40.020 --> 26:43.080
- Stop, just for once today, lying!

26:43.080 --> 26:44.290
Just stay there two seconds.

26:44.290 --> 26:45.583
What the fuck.

26:47.403 --> 26:50.810
Did you have any idea
you're sleeping in that?

26:50.810 --> 26:52.830
- No, not at all.

26:52.830 --> 26:53.663
- I wish you can't see

26:53.663 --> 26:55.730
that kind of stuff.
- I don't wanna sleep in that.

26:55.730 --> 26:56.580
- [Gordon] Brent?

26:59.400 --> 27:00.370
- I see that.

27:00.370 --> 27:02.210
- I want an explanation,

27:02.210 --> 27:05.910
'cause all you've done since
I've arrived here is lie to me.

27:05.910 --> 27:07.990
Lied to me, lied to your staff,

27:07.990 --> 27:11.410
and I am not gonna allow
you to lie to the customers.

27:11.410 --> 27:14.000
- And I totally fucking
disagree with that too.

27:14.000 --> 27:16.502
I have not said one lie to you.

27:16.502 --> 27:17.980
- Yes, you fucking well have.
- I'm not gonna go for that.

27:17.980 --> 27:19.312
- Yes, you have.
- No.

27:19.312 --> 27:20.145
- That is fucking bullshit
- You've been fucking lying

27:20.145 --> 27:21.230
to me all day.

27:21.230 --> 27:22.300
- It's not true.

27:22.300 --> 27:25.750
- You're convinced that
thawed food is fresh food.

27:25.750 --> 27:28.570
You're robbing them of their cash.

27:28.570 --> 27:31.090
You're telling me this
was cleaned a week ago.

27:31.090 --> 27:33.760
Let me ask you question in
front of your customers,

27:33.760 --> 27:34.910
would you sleep on that?

27:34.910 --> 27:35.880
- No.

27:35.880 --> 27:38.040
- So why do you expect them to?

27:38.040 --> 27:39.100
Would you sleep on that?

27:39.100 --> 27:40.150
- No.

27:40.150 --> 27:41.810
- Not an apology.

27:41.810 --> 27:42.643
Nothing.

27:44.630 --> 27:47.323
I'd like to apologise, I'm appalled.

27:48.440 --> 27:49.433
I'm disgusted.

27:50.420 --> 27:51.363
I've had enough.

27:52.870 --> 27:54.570
Anything you'd like to say?

27:54.570 --> 27:57.650
- The pillows like this, I apologise.

27:57.650 --> 28:00.223
- Can I have a word with him
on my own, would you mind?

28:03.810 --> 28:05.520
These guests are hours away

28:05.520 --> 28:08.210
