28:08.210 --> 28:09.823
Blood-stained pillows.

28:10.950 --> 28:13.810
Semen-stained duvet covers,

28:13.810 --> 28:15.530
and sweat

28:15.530 --> 28:17.710
accumulated over years.

28:17.710 --> 28:19.360
- [Brent] I can see that, Gordon.

28:22.440 --> 28:24.210
- I am struggling.

28:24.210 --> 28:26.710
I'm struggling with your
husband that's in denial.

28:26.710 --> 28:28.400
I'm struggling with his arrogance.

28:28.400 --> 28:30.370
And I'm struggling with his blatant lies.

28:30.370 --> 28:32.470
I'm not here to butt heads with a liar.

28:32.470 --> 28:35.323
I'm here to help turn
this business around.

28:36.938 --> 28:37.771
(Afni sighing)

28:37.771 --> 28:39.770
Afni, you can talk to me.

28:39.770 --> 28:41.283
Are you worried about Brent?

28:42.740 --> 28:45.470
