then he got rid of him.

29:24.220 --> 29:25.830
Is that what's bothering him?

29:25.830 --> 29:27.670
Is that why he's in denial?

29:27.670 --> 29:30.510
I need Brent to take his guard down.

29:30.510 --> 29:33.283
Something inside here is bothering him.

29:34.320 --> 29:37.210
I don't know if it's the
financial debt, the pressure.

29:37.210 --> 29:38.210
Is it his son?

29:38.210 --> 29:39.450
I don't know.

29:39.450 --> 29:40.723
I can't get in.

29:43.260 --> 29:44.543
I wanna talk to his son.

29:46.330 --> 29:47.423
How can I get a hold of him?

29:47.423 --> 29:48.940
- I've got his number.

29:48.940 --> 29:50.378
- Thank you.

29:50.378 --> 29:53.960
Afni, you're the only hope I've got.

29:53.960 --> 29:55.315
Can we work together?

29:55.315 --> 29:56.148
- Yeah.

29:56.148 --> 29:58.794
- And can we get him to open up?

29:58.794 --> 29:59.710
- Okay.

29:59.710 --> 30:02.140
- And tomorrow morning, I want the truth

30:02.140 --> 30:03.693
and nothing but the truth.

30:04.556 --> 30:05.389
- Okay.

30:14.840 --> 30:16.940
- I really needed to
break through to Brent

30:16.940 --> 30:18.890
and to see why he is so stubborn.

30:18.890 --> 30:21.300
So my team and I attempted
to get a hold of his son

30:21.300 --> 30:22.950
to meet me at the hotel.

30:22.950 --> 30:24.510
But we were unsuccessful.

30:24.510 --> 30:27.993
Now, it's up to me to try
to get through to Brent.

30:30.200 --> 30:31.890
Let's take a seat at the bar.

30:31.890 --> 30:34.580
I've gotta get through to
you why you're so stubborn.

30:34.580 --> 30:37.503
You got fucked off last night
'cause I mentioned your son.

30:39.370 --> 30:40.833
Why did that hit a nerve?

30:41.740 --> 30:44.480
- You know, we just had a
breakdown in the relationship

30:44.480 --> 30:46.573
when his mom remarried.

