32:06.940 --> 32:07.830
Instead of the other.

32:07.830 --> 32:09.240
- That's never gonna happen.

32:09.240 --> 32:10.218
There's not enough time.

32:10.218 --> 32:13.560
- Well, that's my proudness
and my stubbornness, you know?

32:13.560 --> 32:14.500
- You have to change your ways,

