32:23.330 --> 32:24.163
I'd love you to.

32:24.163 --> 32:25.763
I would so fucking love you to.

32:26.910 --> 32:29.400
And just you calling
them, making an effort,

32:29.400 --> 32:30.580
they need to see the change.

32:30.580 --> 32:32.540
But you need to embrace that.

32:32.540 --> 32:33.373
- [Brent] I agree.

32:33.373 --> 32:34.810
- There's too much at stake.

32:34.810 --> 32:36.490
Reach out to those kids.

32:36.490 --> 32:39.290
You've got to bring those barriers down

32:39.290 --> 32:40.240
and you've gotta open up.

32:40.240 --> 32:43.280
And somewhere in there,
there's the friendly,

32:43.280 --> 32:46.815
comforting, supportive,
you know, astute Brent.

32:46.815 --> 32:47.648
We've gotta get back there.

32:47.648 --> 32:48.481
- Okay.

