And I've been struggling

33:19.740 --> 33:22.520
trying to get through to Brent.

33:22.520 --> 33:23.760
He's in denial.

33:23.760 --> 33:27.060
- I feel like Brent is an undertaker.

33:27.060 --> 33:28.900
Those people that are working for him,

33:28.900 --> 33:32.153
there aren't many that have
very good things to say.

33:33.753 --> 33:35.970
- That's ridiculous.

