and set it on the counter

33:46.790 --> 33:50.640
and went to get a to-go
container, and Afni

33:51.650 --> 33:53.160
scraped it into the garbage.

33:53.160 --> 33:56.380
And she said, my customer
kind of wanted to take that.

33:56.380 --> 34:00.150
And she watched Afni
grab the baked potato,

34:00.150 --> 34:02.622
wipe it off, and grab the steak.

34:02.622 --> 34:03.455
- Out of the trash?

34:03.455 --> 34:05.412
- [Woman] And she made her
give that to the customer.

34:05.412 --> 34:06.245
- No!

34:06.245 --> 34:08.670
