- What do they give back to the town?

34:17.530 --> 34:20.010
- They are absolutely no
part of this community.

34:20.010 --> 34:22.080
They have built walls around themselves

34:22.080 --> 34:25.850
and you need to take care of
each other in the off season.

34:25.850 --> 34:27.570
It's locals taking care of locals.

34:27.570 --> 34:29.980
- You know, I will say,
with the fires, you know,

34:29.980 --> 34:31.540
this whole town came together

34:31.540 --> 34:35.000
